descp2: string, list of string,  or None, default=None Which kind of estimators should be returned. If None, no filter is applied and all estimators are returned.  Possible values are 'classifier', 'regressor', 'cluster' and 'transformer' to get estimators only of these specific types, or a list of these to get the estimators that fit at least one of the types.
